# Allowlist for check-stale-repo-slug.sh
#
# Files listed here MAY contain pre-renumber repo slug references
# (coding-guidelines-v1 .. v14) for legitimate reasons:
#   - changelog/migration history documenting the rename
#   - example URLs in install-script-version-probe specs (v5→v15 is
#     the canonical worked example for the probe algorithm)
#   - generated specTree.json snapshots of the above docs
#   - lovable memory files documenting prior repo identity
#
# Format: one path or glob per line. Lines starting with `#` and blank
# lines are ignored. Matched against repo-relative paths.

# --- changelog & migration history ---
spec/06-seedable-config-architecture/97-changelog.md
CHANGELOG.md

# --- install-script version-probe spec (uses v5→v15 as example) ---
spec/14-update/23-install-script-version-probe.md

# --- generated tree snapshot of above ---
src/data/specTree.json

# --- lovable workspace memory (project identity notes) ---
.lovable/memory/index.md
.lovable/strictly-avoid.md